{"id": 512, "text": "\"Page - 22 - of 68\\n(2)The offer document or 38[term sheet] or any advertisement issued by an issuer in connection with a public issue of debt securities shall not contain any false or misleading statement.\\n39[(3) The offer document or placement memorandum shall contain all material disclosures which are true, correct and adequate to enable the applicants to take an informed investment decision.]\\n40[Utilization of issue proceeds.\\n\"", "meta": {}, "annotation_approver": null, "labels": []}
{"id": 513, "text": "\"18A. (1) The funds raised from issue of municipal debt securities shall be used only for the purposes indicated under the objects stipulated in the offer document or placement memorandum.\\n\"", "meta": {}, "annotation_approver": null, "labels": []}
{"id": 514, "text": "\"(2)Where the proceeds of the issue are earmarked for a defined project or a set of projects, prior requisite approvals, if applicable shall be obtained from the concerned authorities.\\n\"", "meta": {}, "annotation_approver": null, "labels": []}
{"id": 515, "text": "\"(3)The issuers shall maintain a bank account in which the amount raised from the issue shall be immediately transferred after the closure of the issue and such amount shall only be utilised for the indicated project(s):\\n\"", "meta": {}, "annotation_approver": null, "labels": []}
{"id": 516, "text": "\"Provided further that the merchant banker to the issue, in case of private placement, shall confirm to the bankers to the issue by way of copies of listing and trading approvals that all formalities in connection with the issue have been completed and that the banker is free to release the money to the issuer or release the money for refund in case of failure of the issue.\\n\"", "meta": {}, "annotation_approver": null, "labels": []}
{"id": 517, "text": "\"(4)The issuer shall disclose the schedule of implementation of the project in the offer document or placement memorandum in a tabular form and the funds raised by the issuer shall be utilized in accordance with the said Schedule.\\n\"", "meta": {}, "annotation_approver": null, "labels": []}
{"id": 518, "text": "\"36 Inserted by the Securities and Exchange Board of India (Issue and Listing of Debt Securities by Municipalities) (Amendment) Regulations, 2019 w.e.f. 27.09.2019.\\n\"", "meta": {}, "annotation_approver": null, "labels": []}
